Class WiFi

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.game.WiFi

  • public class WiFi
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the data that will be fetched from the server before the start of the game. It uses the Wifi connection class to fetch data from the server Based off example written by Michael Smith and Tharsan Ponnampalam
    Author:
    Lara Kollokian
